description.displayText: Tanisha began to take care of my daughter when she was around 3 months old. She took the best care of her for almost 2 years. When I came home from work, my daughter was always happy and smiling. Tanisha was always on time and would help out in a pinch. She had my daughter on a routine in no time. Tanisha was our only choice for our daughter! Our family loves Tanisha!

description.displayText: I have known Tanisha for many years. And when I had my son she took excellent care of him. I left for work knowing my child was in good hands. Always on time, Reliable, and if I needed her to stay late she never had a problem doing so. So everyone out there read her Bio. You will no be disappointed. My family and I adore her..!

description.displayText: Tanisha has been our caregiver for many years working with our children as infants and as they've grown up.  She is responsible and on time for work whenever I've needed her and gone out of her way to help me and my husband out when situations arose that were beyond her normal work hours.  She's great working with kids, helping them with their homework, feeding them, keeping them clean and organized.  We have been very lucky to have her taking care of our children.
